spec_data.Name: python2-wcwidth
spec_data.Description:
This API is mainly for Terminal Emulator implementors, or those writing programs
that expect to interpreted by a terminal emulator and wish to determine the
printable width of a string on a Terminal.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 05:03:32 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Measures number of Terminal column cells of wide-character codes
